{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Blue Sky Realty</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #007bff; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.7), rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/007bff/ffffff?text=Beautiful+Homes');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #007bff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #fff;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #007bff;\n        }\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            flex-basis: 30%;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #007bff;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        .contact {\n            background-color: #e9ecef;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        /* Font Awesome for icons - include this in a real project, for this example we'll skip it for simplicity */\n        /* You'd typically link a CDN here: <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\"> */\n        .icon-placeholder { /* Placeholder for icons */\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 50px;\n            height: 50px;\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            line-height: 50px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"hero\">\n            <h1>Blue Sky Realty</h1>\n            <p>Your dream home is just a click away.</p>\n            <a href=\"#listings\" class=\"btn\">View Properties</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Contact Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"listings\">\n        <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\u2605</div>\n                <h3>Modern Family Home</h3>\n                <p>Spacious 4-bedroom house with a large garden. Perfect for families.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\u2605</div>\n                <h3>Downtown Loft</h3>\n                <p>Sleek 2-bedroom loft with city views. Ideal for urban living.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"icon-placeholder\">\u2605</div>\n                <h3>Seaside Cottage</h3>\n                <p>Charming 3-bedroom cottage with ocean access. Relax and unwind.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" style=\"background-color: #f0f8ff;\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">At Blue Sky Realty, we are dedicated to helping you find the perfect property. Our experienced agents provide personalized service and market expertise to make your real estate journey smooth and successful. We believe in transparency, integrity, and building lasting relationships.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Blue Sky Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}